org.apache.paimon.hive.mapred

Class PaimonRecordReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.paimon.hive.mapred.PaimonRecordReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, org.apache.hadoop.mapred.RecordReader<Void,RowDataContainer>

    public class PaimonRecordReader
extends Object
implements org.apache.hadoop.mapred.RecordReader<Void,RowDataContainer>
    Base RecordReader for paimon. Reads KeyValues from data files and picks out InternalRow for Hive to consume.

    NOTE: To support projection push down, when selectedColumns does not match columnNames this reader will still produce records of the original schema. However, columns not in selectedColumns will be null.
